      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROCK REVOLUTION (2) is worth another chance. Had first run here last time when led but swallowed up late and was safely held. Senior rider goes on and small field suits. Take catching. LEVERAGED BUYOUT (1) remains the one to beat. Has won the last three, the latest open class here beating a few rivals from today. More weight but hard to fault and looks a top chance again. GRINZINGER TUNDRA (4) was fourth behind him last time and meets the winner far better at the weights. Fitter again and can improve sharply. Likewise. GARRIX (3) finished third in the same weight and also is far better off at the weights. Must include. D'AMBIDEX (5) is still a maiden but has speed and can give a sight at odds.",
